urlText: L1 Leichhardt North lift out of service
content:
The lift at Leichhardt North light rail stop on the L1 Dulwich Hill Line is temporarilly out of service until further notice.
 
For your safety, do not use even if doors open.
 
Alternative access:
  • Use the stairs, if able to
  • Or use the opposite accessible entry/exit pathway via Charles Street.
     
For urgent assistance:
  • Use the Help Point if on the platform
  • Or call 131 500
